---
description: SuperAgent TDD discipline — write tests before implementation
globs: ["**/*.test.*", "**/*.spec.*", "**/test/**", "**/__tests__/**"]
alwaysApply: false
---

# Test-Driven Development

1. Write failing test FIRST
2. Implement minimum code to pass
3. Refactor while green
4. Never skip — even for "simple" changes
5. Run tests before declaring done
